title: TRIPLE NUTRITION CURL NOURISH BUTTER CREAM I GARNIER FRUCTIS
description:
Do your curls crave moisture that lasts? Treat them with Garnier Fructis Curl Nourish Butter Cream. The leave-in treatment with coconut oil infuses hair with 3 days of lasting moisture* for stronger, more nourished curls.

*Using Garnier Fructis Curl Nourish Shampoo, Conditioner & Leave-In Treatment vs. non-conditioning shampoo.
